== Events == * {{ill|Shōgen|ja|正元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1259]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Shōka|ja|正嘉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Shōgen|ja|正元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Meitoku|ja|明徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year / {{ill|Genchū|ja|元中|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1390]] {{ill|April 12|ja|4月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Kōō|ja|康応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Meitoku|ja|明徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1829]] {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In connection with the Siebold incident, a new death sentence was pronounced against {{ill|Takahashi Kageyasu|ja|高橋景保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, who had been imprisoned. * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1867]] {{ill|April 30|ja|4月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate received the steam warship “{{ill|Kaiyōmaru|ja|開陽丸|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}” on order from the Netherlands.
== Births == {{Expand section}}
== Deaths == * {{ill|Entoku|ja|延徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1489]] {{ill|April 26|ja|4月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshinobu|ja|足利義尚|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 9th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (born [[1465]])<ref>{{Kotobank|足利義尚}}</ref>. * {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1646]] {{ill|May 11|ja|5月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yagyū Munenori|ja|柳生宗矩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Kenjutsu master and father of {{ill|Yagyū Sanjūrō|ja|柳生三厳（十兵衛）|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[1571]]).
