== Deaths == * {{ill|Entoku|ja|延徳|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1489]] {{ill|April 26|ja|4月26日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshinobu|ja|足利義尚|qq=}}, the 9th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (born [[1465]])<ref>{{Kotobank|足利義尚|qq=}}</ref>. * {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1646]] {{ill|May 11|ja|5月11日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Yagyū Munenori|ja|柳生宗矩|qq=}}, a Kenjutsu master and father of {{ill|Yagyū Sanjūrō|ja|柳生三厳（十兵衛）|qq=}} (born [[1571]]).
