* {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1646]] {{ill|May 11|ja|5月11日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yagyū Munenori|ja|柳生宗矩|qq=|12=draft}}, a Kenjutsu master and father of {{ill|Yagyū Sanjūrō|ja|柳生三厳（十兵衛）|qq=|12=draft}} (born [[1571]]).

