{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=三月廿六|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 3월 26일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 26''' is the 26th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Shōgen|ja|正元|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1259]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Shōka|ja|正嘉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to {{ill|Shōgen|ja|正元|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Meitoku|ja|明徳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year / {{ill|Genchū|ja|元中|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1390]] {{ill|April 12|ja|4月12日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Kōō|ja|康応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to {{ill|Meitoku|ja|明徳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1829]] {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – In connection with the Siebold incident, a new death sentence was pronounced against {{ill|Takahashi Kageyasu|ja|高橋景保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, who had been imprisoned. * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1867]] {{ill|April 30|ja|4月30日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate received the steam warship “{{ill|Kaiyōmaru|ja|開陽丸|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}” on order from the Netherlands.
== Births == {{Expand section|qq=}}
== Deaths == * {{ill|Entoku|ja|延徳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1489]] {{ill|April 26|ja|4月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshinobu|ja|足利義尚|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 9th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (born [[1465]])<ref>{{Kotobank|足利義尚|qq=}}</ref>. * {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1646]] {{ill|May 11|ja|5月11日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Yagyū Munenori|ja|柳生宗矩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a Kenjutsu master and father of {{ill|Yagyū Sanjūrō|ja|柳生三厳（十兵衛）|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (born [[1571]]).
