'''March 26''' is the 26th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Butsumetsu|1=Butsumetsu|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q10886789}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Shōgen|ja|正元|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōgen|1=Q11123303|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11123303}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1259|en|1259|qid=Q5507|lt=1259|1=1259}} {{ill|April 20|en|April 20|qid=Q2524|lt=April 20|1=April 20}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Shōka (era)|en|Shōka (era)|qid=Q1327489|lt=Shōka|1=Shōka (era)}} to {{ill|Shōgen|ja|正元|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōgen|1=Q11123303|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11123303}}.
* {{ill|Meitoku|en|Meitoku|qid=Q1145032|lt=Meitoku|1=Meitoku}} 1st year / {{ill|Genchū|en|Genchū|qid=Q1146236|lt=Genchū|1=Genchū}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1390|en|1390|qid=Q6375|lt=1390|1=1390}} {{ill|April 12|en|April 12|qid=Q2499|lt=April 12|1=April 12}}) – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Kōō|en|Kōō|qid=Q1146172|lt=Kōō|1=Kōō}} to {{ill|Meitoku|en|Meitoku|qid=Q1145032|lt=Meitoku|1=Meitoku}}.
* {{ill|Bunsei|en|Bunsei|qid=Q1327119|lt=Bunsei|1=Bunsei}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1829|en|1829|qid=Q7572|lt=1829|1=1829}} {{ill|April 29|en|April 29|qid=Q2535|lt=April 29|1=April 29}}) – In connection with the Siebold incident, a new death sentence was pronounced against {{ill|Takahashi Kageyasu|ja|高橋景保|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takahashi Kageyasu|1=Takahashi Kageyasu|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11671324}}, who had been imprisoned.
* {{ill|Keiō|en|Keiō|qid=Q776775|lt=Keiō|1=Keiō}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1867|en|1867|qid=Q7715|lt=1867|1=1867}} {{ill|April 30|en|April 30|qid=Q2536|lt=April 30|1=April 30}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate received the steam warship “{{ill|Japanese frigate Kaiyō Maru|en|Japanese frigate Kaiyō Maru|qid=Q3005167|lt=Kaiyōmaru|1=Japanese frigate Kaiyō Maru}}” on order from the Netherlands.

