== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Entoku|en|Entoku|qid=Q431465|lt=Entoku|1=Entoku}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1489|en|1489|qid=Q6665|lt=1489|1=1489}} {{ill|April 26|en|April 26|qid=Q2532|lt=April 26|1=April 26}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshihisa|en|Ashikaga Yoshihisa|qid=Q447639|lt=Ashikaga Yoshinobu|1=Ashikaga Yoshihisa}}, the 9th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (born {{ill|1465|en|1465|qid=Q6556|lt=1465|1=1465}})<ref>{{Kotobank|足利義尚|qq=}}</ref>.
* {{ill|Shōhō|en|Shōhō|qid=Q1146192|lt=Shōhō|1=Shōhō}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1646|en|1646|qid=Q6930|lt=1646|1=1646}} {{ill|May 11|en|May 11|qid=Q2558|lt=May 11|1=May 11}}) – {{ill|Yagyū Munenori|en|Yagyū Munenori|qid=Q631099|lt=Yagyū Munenori|1=Yagyū Munenori}}, a Kenjutsu master and father of {{ill|Yagyū Sanjūrō|ja|柳生三厳（十兵衛）|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yagyū Sanjūrō|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} (born {{ill|1571|en|1571|qid=Q6666|lt=1571|1=1571}}).

